黜臭」</span> （白話字：Thuh-chh&agrave;u），「黜」為揭發之意，揭發他人臭處，意為「揭人短處」，後來以華語的諧音「吐槽」為借用字來取代台語的發音，成為了台灣流行語，即指不給面子的反駁行為。由於日本動漫在<span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>的流行，所以吐槽也隨着台灣的翻譯散播被廣泛運用各大ACG社群，如Acfun和bilibili等，並成為了網絡熱詞。但中文中的吐槽相對於日文，除了拆台外，還有發牢騷的意思。各大媒體新聞也經常把「吐槽」用於新聞的標題。"},{"pid":"d78ddb2fd1610f9d9fb1b88495fae76ebed44fb0","tid":692584,"uid":92017,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5130fdf4cacfed94993c5295152c9186c6b2f1b7","tid":692584,"uid":104422,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"6fa164fb74c165f4d5f2ec19d5cf041f55151869","tid":692584,"uid":136770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T20:30:46.000Z","msg":"吐糟，鬼點子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死返上大陸啦大陸喱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T20:33:30.000Z","msg":"um.....<br />\n不如你話比我知源自日本既吐糟可以點譯返做廣東話好嗎?<br />\n<strong>日本</strong>都係大陸黎嫁咩?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T20:39:23.000Z","msg":"吐糟：講野好mean、窒人好勁，或者係講野好絕核/抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wiki都有講吐糟係香港個應用情況啦，umm乜鳩<br />\n鬼點子：古靈精怪、鬼主意<br />\n<br />\n真係好怕d人生搬硬套外來用話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前排已經聽到有香港youtuber親口講「看三小」，遲d係咪連八格耶魯都要直接用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee66e6ff72d2d4118372c3060abf278d8d7fa52e","tid":692584,"uid":58165,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T20:39:44.000Z","msg":"樓主牛逼"},{"pid":"5f3ac465c740363c1054eb757f4740c9dc0bf471","tid":692584,"uid":104422,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"519ffdaaa0966872431540b7dcc59ccefdbce0e0","tid":692584,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T20:37:56.000Z","msg":"咩比賽 咩類型既片<img s